data.description: This remarkable residence redefines modern living with its thoughtful design and luxurious features. This 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home boasts a 3-car garage, loft, dining room and den - providing a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, versatility and one of the largest homes in the neighborhood. Upon entering, you're greeted with a spacious open-plan living area, graced with premium hardwood floors and ample natural light. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, sleek granite countertops and a large island for social gatherings. Relax in the magnificent primary suite, complete with a walk-in closet and a spa-like 5 piece en-suite bathroom. The additional bedrooms offer flexibility and comfort, suitable for family, guests, or a home office. The loft area adds versatility to the home, offering a space that can be customized to suit your lifestyle. Create a cozy reading nook, a play area, or an additional workspace – the possibilities are endless. Step outside to the expansive zeroscaped backyard, complete with a beautiful huge patio, perfect for outdoor entertainment or peaceful evenings. Enjoy the fresh air and make the most of your private outdoor retreat. The 3 car attached garage provides plenty of space for vehicles and storage. This home is within a short distance of local parks, golf course, shopping centers, and a variety of dining options. Experience the best of suburban living with urban conveniences close by. This is an ideal place to live. Conveniently located, you are just a short drive from entertainment, cultural experiences, and professional opportunities. Don't miss the chance to own this magnificent property at 12274 Joplin Street. https://v6d.com/houses/12274-joplin-st-brighton-co-80603/
